700
00:35:17,040 --> 00:35:18,400
Send some people quickly

701
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:19,760
to take down that vulgar woman.

702
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:21,640
Mother, it's not a big deal.

703
00:35:21,720 --> 00:35:23,880
