777
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:23,200
- My belt!
- It's mine now.

778
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:25,120
- It's mine now.
- My belt.

779
00:38:25,200 --> 00:38:26,360
Stop.

780
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:28,640
- Be careful, young master.
